Package com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.edfexamples.common

This package provides functionality shared by EDF examples.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DirectoryHandler
    This is the source directory handler for the UPA EDF consumer application.
    EDFChannelSession
    Manages UPA EDF channel and provides methods for connection establishment, channel initialization, read, and write methods for EDF consumer example.
    EDFWatchList
    Watchlist used by the EDFConsumer application.
    MarketByOrderHandler
    This is the market by order handler for the UPA consumer application.
    MarketByPriceHandler
    This is the market by price handler for the UPA consumer application.
    MarketPriceHandler
    This is the market price handler for the UPA consumer application.
    MsgQueue
    Message queue used by the EDFConsumer application.
    StreamIdWatchList
    This is a hash map based WatchList for quick lookup of item states when response is received.
    StreamIdWatchList.WatchListEntry
    Watch list entry used by StreamIdWatchList.
